arrsbar.co.uk/ |archive-date=5 January 2013 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Morganite\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.morganitecrucible.com/ |title=Morganite Crucible |access-date=23 November 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801191536/http://www.morganitecrucible.com/ |archive-date=1 August 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Museum\">{{Cite web |title=History of Worcester Royal Infirmary to Be Brought Back to Life |publisher=[[University of Worcester]] |date=5 November 2009 |url=http://www.worcester.ac.uk/discover/history-of-worcester-royal-infirmary-to-be-brought-back-to-life.html |accessdate=8 January 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703105200/http://www.worcester.ac.uk/discover/history-of-worcester-royal-infirmary-to-be-brought-back-to-life.html |archive-date=3 July 2017 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"news.bbc.co.uk\">{{Cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/herefordandworcester/hi/people_and_places/nature/newsid_8940000/8940615.stm |title=Extreme weather in Herefordshire and Worcestershire |publisher=BBC |accessdate=12 January 2012 |date=20 September 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121202174046/http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/herefordandworcester/hi/people_and_places/nature/newsid_8940000/8940615.stm |archive-date=2 December 2012 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Porcelain Museum\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.worcesterporcelainmuseum.org.uk |title=Worcester Porcelain Museum |publisher=Worcester Porcelain Museum |date= |accessdate=27 September 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100919235209/http://www.worcesterporcelainmuseum.org.uk/ |archive-date=19 September 2010 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RIBA\">{{Cite web |title=Royal Institute of British Architects |publisher=Royal Institute of British Architects |url=http://www.ribapix.com/index.php?a=wordsearch&s=item&key=WczoyMToiSm9obiBBbGV4YW5kZXIgY2luZW1hIjs=&pg=21 |accessdate=7 January 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\