ather in Herefordshire and Worcestershire |publisher=BBC |accessdate=12 January 2012 |date=20 September 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121202174046/http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/herefordandworcester/hi/people_and_places/nature/newsid_8940000/8940615.stm |archive-date=2 December 2012 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Porcelain Museum\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.worcesterporcelainmuseum.org.uk |title=Worcester Porcelain Museum |publisher=Worcester Porcelain Museum |date= |accessdate=27 September 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100919235209/http://www.worcesterporcelainmuseum.org.uk/ |archive-date=19 September 2010 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RIBA\">{{Cite web |title=Royal Institute of British Architects |publisher=Royal Institute of British Architects |url=http://www.ribapix.com/index.php?a=wordsearch&s=item&key=WczoyMToiSm9obiBBbGV4YW5kZXIgY2luZW1hIjs=&pg=21 |accessdate=7 January 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Shropshire\">{{Cite web |title=Ann Julia Kemble Hatton (1764\u20131848) |publisher=Literary Heritage West Midlands |url=http://www3.shropshire-cc.gov.uk/hatton.htm |accessdate=8 January 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617204945/http://www3.shropshire-cc.gov.uk/hatton.htm |archive-date=17 June 2013 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"WorcesterGloveMaking\">{{Cite web |title=Worcester glove-making |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/ahistoryoftheworld/objects/ftRyrzGHSdqjcFiBLdgwGA |publisher=BBC |accessdate=18 January 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306065729/http://www.bbc.co.uk/ahistoryoftheworld/objects/ftRyrzGHSdqjcFiBLdgwGA |archive-date=6 March 2012 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Worcester News\">{{Cite news |author=Lauren Rogers |date=21 September 2007 |url=http://www.worcesternews.co.uk/display.var.1706462.0.beaten_tory_keeps_a_low_profile.php |title=Beaten Tory Keeps A Low Profile |newspaper=[[Worcester News]] |access-date=30 September 2007 |archive-url=https://web.a